meback%20In%20A%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20the%20beginning%20and%20end%20of%202024%20could%20not%20have%20been%20more%20different.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20month%20into%20the%20year%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20leader%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20land%20scam%20case%20and%20he%20had%20made%20sure%20he%20resigned%20as%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20before%20he%20was%20arrested.%20Now%2C%20with%20a%20month%20left%20in%20the%20year%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20architect%20of%20a%20thumping%20victory%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20remains%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20and%20he%20gets%20a%20second%20straight%20term%20as%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JMM%20leader%20also%20suffered%20multiple%20other%20setbacks%20in%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Soren's%20arrest%20on%20January%2031%2C%20his%20sister-in-law%2C%20Sita%20Soren%20-%20the%20wife%20of%20his%20late%20brother%20Durga%20Soren%20-%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20March.%20She%20was%20miffed%20over%20alleged%20moves%20to%20make%20Mr%20Soren's%20wife%2C%20Kalpana%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20his%20absence%20and%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20JMM%20for%20'anti-party'%20activities%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20chief%20minister%20was%20then%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20Jharkhand%20High%20Court%20in%20June%2C%20five%20months%20after%20his%20arrest.%20The%20court%20held%20that%2C%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20was%20not%20guilty%20and%20was%20not%20likely%20to%20commit%20a%20similar%20offence%2C%20noting%20that%20both%20conditions%20for%20bail%20under%20the%20stringent%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20had%20been%20met.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChampai%20Soren%20-%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20JMM%20chief%20Shibu%20Soren%20and%20widely%20seen%20as%20the%20number%20three%20in%20the%20party%20-%20was%20appointed%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20Hemant%20Soren's%20absence.%20Trouble%20began%20brewing%2C%20however%2C%20when%20the%20party%20asked%20him%20to%20resign%20in%20July%20after%20Mr%20Soren's%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20leadership%20had%20changed%2C%20I%20was%20given%20responsibility.%20You%20know%20the%20sequence%20of%20events.%20After%20Hemant%20Soren%20came%20back%2C%20we%20(the%20coalition)%20picked%20him%20as%20our%20leader%20and%20I%20have%20resigned.%20I%20am%20following%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20coalition%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20upset%20Champai%20Soren%20had%20said%20after%20resigning%20in%20July.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20the%20BJP%20a%20month%20later%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bhumiliated%20and%20insulted%26quot%3B%20and%20wanted%20to%20deliver%20justice%20to%20the%20people.%20The%20BJP%20also%20accused%20the%20JMM-Congress%20alliance%20of%20allowing%20%26quot%3Binfiltration%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20state%2C%20an%20issue%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20gaining%20traction%20among%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20this%2C%20and%20some%20seat-sharing%20trouble%20with%20allies%20like%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20ensured%20that%20his%20party%20bettered%20its%20tally%20to%2034%20this%20year%20in%20the%2081-member%20Assembly%2C%20up%20from%2030%20in%202019.%20Good%20performances%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20RJD%20and%20CPI%20(ML)%20have%20taken%20the%20ruling%20coalition's%20number%20to%2056%2C%20with%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%20winning%20only%2024%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732412940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fq43dsmj8_hemant-soren_625x300_23_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjailers-box-to-ballot-box-hemant-soren-scripts-2nd-comeback-in-a-year-7086895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20the%20beginning%20and%20end