h%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cormarie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224565%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb5fafb4912df3ae1b1176%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223205%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%3Cp%3EContributor%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f944e72b-8be1-4a54-b2f1-cd3c72a7b4a5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUkraine%20NATO%20deal%20in%20doubt%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20a%20prospective%20Trump%20peace%20deal%20in%20Ukraine%20are%20unclear%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20appear%20likely%20to%20include%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20joining%20the%20NATO%20alliance%20that%20could%20best%20guarantee%20its%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%20has%20said%20that%20as%20a%20condition%20of%20any%20peace%20deal%2C%20Ukraine%20must%20agree%20to%20remain%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20comments%20before%20the%20election%20by%20JD%20Vance%2C%20Trump's%20running%20mate%2C%20suggested%20that%20Trump%20might%20agree%20to%20the%20demand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F09%2F13%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fvance-trump-ukraine-russia-war.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20Vance%20remarking%20t%3C%2Fa%3Ehat%20Russia%20would%20get%20a%20%26quot%3Bguarantee%20of%20neutrality%26quot%3B%20from%20Ukraine%20as%20part%20of%20a%20likely%20deal.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20may%20appear%20to%20neatly%20sidestep%20the%20issue%20that%20some%20claim%20lies%20behind%20Russia's%20Ukraine%20invasion%3A%20Preventing%20the%20eastward%20expansion%20of%20NATO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%2C%20however%2C%20say%20that%20such%20a%20deal%20could%20further%20embolden%20Putin%20and%20ignores%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Russian%20president's%20real%20motive%20is%20imperialist%20conquest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkyivindependent.com%2Fopinion-jd-vances-neutrality-pitch-for-ukraine-is-a-shortcut-to-putins-next-invasion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20Kyiv%20Independent%20in%20October%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3ETimothy%20Ash%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20London's%20Chatham%20House%20think%20tank%2C%20said%20Ukraine%20was%20effectively%20neutral%20until%20Russia's%20first%20invasion%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIts%20military%20weakness%20and%20neutrality%20were%20a%20green%20light%20for%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20to%20annex%20and%20invade%20Ukrainian%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20such%20a%20status%20would%20deter%20Putin%20from%20attacking%20again.%20The%20only%20assurance%20against%20further%20Russian%20aggression%20is%20a%20strong%20defense%2C%20ideally%20in%20alliance%20with%20Western%20partners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205ae4f1e-05c9-4385-b995-48e97a6260d6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20would%20a%20security%20deal%20look%20like%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Trump%20takes%20Ukrainian%20NATO%C2%A0membership%20off%20the%20table%2C%20a%20different%20type%20of%20security%20deal%20could%20still%20be%20negotiated%2C%20said%20Cormarie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20European%20allies%20could%20take%20a%20leading%20role%20in%20helping%20defend%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMargus%20Tsahkna%2C%20Estonia's%20foreign%20minister%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F98ceca6c-cad3-44e1-82ec-e0df71bd241c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Financial%20Times%20this%20%3C%2Fa%3Eweek%20that%20troops%20from%20Ukraine's%20European%20allies%20could%20be%20deployed%20to%20the%20country%20to%20deter%20Russian%20attacks%20as%20part%20of%20a%20Trump-brokered%20deal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECormarie%20said%20another%20option%20would%20be%20to%20massively%20boost%20Ukraine's%20capacity%20to%20defend%20itself%20from%20attack%20through%20a%20US%20foreign%20military%20financing%20program.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202014%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20overhauled%20its%20military%2C%20and%20now%20has%20an%20expanding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwestern-defense-companies-set-up-operations-in-ukraine-war-continues-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20industrial%20sector%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eproducing%20equipment%20ranging%20from%20missiles%20to%20sophisticated%20drones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20a%20weak%20substitute%20for%20support%20from%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20military%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20truce%20containing%20a%20watered-down%20security%20deal%20for%20Ukraine%20would%20likely%20only%20mean%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20war%20while%20Russia%20regathers%20its%20strength.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20less%20strong%20these%20commitments%20are%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20this%20agreement%20would%20only%20be%20a%20truce%20before%20Moscow%20takes%20another%20'bite'%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20Kyiv%2C%26quot%3B%20Cormarie%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-might-able-ukraine-russia-stop-fighting-real-peace-harder-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732381741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67406d8aede4eeae3928f412%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-might-able-ukraine-russia-stop-fighting-real-peace-harder-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20peace%20deal%20could%20be%20fragile%20unless%20Ukraine%20gets%20security%20guanrantees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A121%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-might-able-ukraine-russia-stop-fighting-real-peace-harder-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Congress'%20Troll%20Politics%20Leads%20To%20MVA's%20Downfall%20In%20Maharashtra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20mandate%20is%20a%20rare%20phenomenon%20and%20a%20powerful%20lesson%2C%20prompting%20political%20parties%2C%20analysts%2C%20and%20commentators%20to%20return%20to%20the%20drawing%20board.%20This%20paradigm%20shift%20will%20take%20time%20to%20fully%20comprehend%20-%20and%20what%20a%20shift%20it%20has%20been!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20delivering%20a%20decisive%20majority%20to%20the%20NDA%20is%20stunningly%20historic.%20For%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20this%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%2C%20achieved%20through%20years%20of%20hard%20work%20to%20establish%20itself%20independently%2C%20without%20relying%20on%20the%20support%20of%20regional%20parties.%20While%20the%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20not%20yet%20fully%20realised%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20taken%20a%20major%20step%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra's%20voters%2C%20who%20have%20experienced%20coalition%20governments%20for%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20now%20seem%20to%20have%20opted%20for%20greater%20stability%2C%20while%20technically%20remaining%20in%20the%20years%20of%20coalition%20era.%20With%20the%20BJP%20securing%20130%2B%20seats%2C%20the%20party%20has%20positioned%20itself%20as%20a%20force%20less%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20pulls%20and%20pressures%20of%20running%20a%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20can%20be%20written%20about%20the%20factors%20that%20contributed%20to%20the%20BJP's%20success%2C%20but%20the%20essence%20is%20straightforward%3A%20the%20party%20has%20been%20quick%20to%20learn%20from%20its%20mistakes%20and%20failures%2C%20understood%20the%20pulse%20of%20the%20people%2C%20and%20executed%20a%20bold%2C%20high-stakes%20strategy%20under%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo.%20Their%20unique%20brand%20of%20social%20engineering%20has%20yielded%20instant%20results%2C%20garnering%20both%20Maratha%20and%20non-Maratha%20votes.%20Achieving%20this%20level%20of%20finesse%20in%20such%20a%20short%20time%20offers%20a%20masterclass%20in%20political%20strategy%20-%20one%20that%20calls%20for%20admiration%20and%20study%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20secured%20a%20larger%20share%20of%20OBC%2C%20SC%2C%20and%20ST%20votes%20across%20most%20of%20the%20six%20political%20regions.%20Women%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Ladki%20Behna%20scheme%20played%20a%20vital%20role%2C%20and%20the%20RSS%20lent%20its%20discipline%20machine%20more%20generously%20to%20bolster%20the%20already%20formidable%20and%20finely%20tuned%20BJP%20election%20machinery.%20The%20recent%20Haryana%20assembly%20election%20victory%20put%20a%20spring%20in%20their%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20shift%20focus%20to%20the%20MVA's%20dramatic%20collapse.%20From%20a%20position%20of%20strength%2C%20it%20fell%20apart%20in%20just%20five%20months%20-%20a%20stunning%20reversal%20after%20its%20strong%20performance%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20debacle%20serves%20as%20a%20serious%20lesson%20in%20how%20to%20let%20opportunities%20slip%20away.%20The%20MVA%20lost%20an%20election%20it%20could%20have%20won%20with%20minimal%20effort%2C%20and%20just%20swept%20away%20in%20a%20political%20tsunami%20it%20failed%20to%20anticipate.%20It's%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20need%20to%20stay%20connected%20with%20the%20ground%20and%20its%20'janata'%20(people).%20Humility%20to%20at%20least%20acknowledge%20missteps%20and%20serious%20introspection%20are%20urgently%20recommended%20for%20them%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20struggle%20to%20recall%20any%20of%20their%20political%20messages%20resonating%20with%20voters%20anywhere%20in%20the%20state.%20Not%20a%20single%20one.%20The%20MVA%20seemed%20stuck%20in%20a%20loop%20of%20recycled%20tape-vague%20schemes%2C%20half-hearted%20promises%2C%20and%20relentless%20negativity.%20Statements%20like%20'Samvidhan%20khatre%20mein%20hai%20(The%20Constitution%20is%20in%20danger)'%2C%20accusations%20against%20opponents%2C%20and%20calls%20for%20caste%20censuses%20dominated%20their%20narrative.%20Add%20to%20that%20a%20fair%20bit%20of%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20and%20you%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20voters%20just%20switched%20them%20off.%20The%20endless%20barrage%20of%20negative%20sentiments%20alienated%20voters%20who%20had%20clearly%20moved%20on%2C%20leaving%20the%20MVA%20clueless%20about%20the%20big%20change%20underway%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20MVA%20offer%20even%20a%20single%20story%20to%20enthuse%20voters%3F%20I%20can%20recall%20none.%20Their%20campaign%20lacked%20focus%2C%20vision%2C%20and%20an%20inspiring%20message%20-%20some%20of%20the%20common%20elements%20find%20in%20parties%20that%20are%20ready%20to%20learn%20and%20not%20gloss%20over%20slips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20needs%20to%20understand%20that%20its%20de%20facto%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20failed%20to%20deliver%20thus%20far.%20His%20personal%20obsessions%20get%20the%20better%20of%20him%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20preventing%20him%20from%20crafting%20the%20broad%20political%20platform%20India%20expects%20from%20a%20national%20opposition%20party.%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20fell%20into%20the%20same%20trap.%20Only%20Sharad%20Pawar%20offered%20a%20narrative%20that%20resonated%20with%20voters%2C%20but%20the%20noise%20generated%20by%20Gandhi%20and%20Thackeray%20overshadowed%20any%20meaningful%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20and%20Thackeray%2C%20for%20reasons%20best%20known%20to%20them%2C%20focused%20their%20campaign%20on%20Dharavi%2C%20as%20if%20they%20were%20contesting%20a%20municipal%20ward%20election%20or%20campaigning%20for%20a%20single%20assembly%20constituency%2C%20rather%20than%20addressing%20the%20other%20287%20seats%20in%20the%20large%20and%20very%20important%20state%20of%20Maharashtra.%20They%20failed%20to%20recognise%20that%20voters%20in%20the%20state%20are%20attuned%20to%20the%20larger%20national%20picture%20and%20eager%20to%20reclaim%20Maharashtra's%20prime%20position%20among%20India's%20galloping%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20puzzling%20why%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20harbours%20a%20personal%20obsession%20with%20targeting%20a%20first-generation%20entrepreneur%2C%20especially%20when%20such%20posturing%20fails%20to%20translate%20into%20votes%20for%20his%20party.%20He%20must%20also%20know%20that%2062%20percent%20of%20even%20MVA%20voters%20want%20their%20Dharavi%20to%20become%20the%20pride%20of%20place%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20anti-business%20stance%20was%20rejected%20by%20Maharashtra%20voters%2C%20who%20see%20it%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20agenda-perhaps%20influenced%20by%20corporate%20rivalries%20or%20external%20forces%20jealous%20of%20India's%20accelerated%20ascent%20now.%20This%20perception%20has%20damaged%20Gandhi's%20credibility%2C%20as%20voters%20increasingly%20see%20his%20actions%20as%20not%20very%20conducive%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20India%20it%20is%20getting%20ready%20to%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndians%20have%20consistently%20demonstrated%20their%20desire%20for%20a%20robust%20democracy%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20strong%20opposition%20to%20keep%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20check.%20The%20outcome%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20exhibited%20that%20democratic%20instinct.%20However%2C%20the%20risk%20to%20democracy%20doesn't%20come%20from%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20or%20the%20RSS%20-%20it%20stems%20from%20the%20Congress's%20inability%20to%20effectively%20play%20its%20role%20as%20a%20responsible%20opposition%20party.%20Regional%20parties%2C%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20are%20playing%20this%20role%20more%20effectively.%20And%20they%20are%20winning%20elections%20too%2C%20and%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20results%20have%20further%20diminished%20any%20lingering%20hope%20that%20the%20Congress%20can%20rise%20to%20the%20challenges.%20The%20party%20s