0in%20the%20doomsday%20prepper%20aspect%20or%20the%20idea%20of%20preparing%20to%20survive%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20catastrophe.%20I'm%20not%20a%20full%20doomsday%20prepper%2C%20but%20I%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20prepared%20for%20the%20unknown%2C%20including%20having%20food%20storage%20and%20some%20survival%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20talk%20to%20the%20hardcore%20preppers%2C%20which%20I'm%20not%2C%20missile%20silos%20are%20not%20that%20great%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20you%20think%20is%20the%20worst-case%20scenario.%20If%20it's%20a%20Walking-Dead-style%20apocalypse%2C%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20missile%20silo%20because%20then%20you're%20trapped%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%2030%25%20of%20my%20interest%20was%20in%20the%20modern%20archaeology%20aspect%20of%20owning%20something%20like%20this.%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20dig%20it%20up%20and%20see%20what%20was%20in%20there.%20Initially%2C%20I%20intended%20to%20make%20it%20a%20house%20for%20my%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20owning%20a%20missile%20silo%20because%20it's%20just%20kick%20ass.%20The%20place%20has%207%2C000-pound%20doors.%20Its%20three%20floors%20are%20made%20out%20of%20a%20steel%20structure%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20birdcage.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20on%20eight%20springs%20and%20actually%20hangs%20from%20the%20ceiling.%20And%20the%20reason%20is%20if%20it%20gets%20hit%20by%20a%20bomb%2C%20it%20allows%20the%20structure%20to%20shake%20to%20try%20to%20preserve%20the%20equipment%20and%20the%20people%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20rattle%20space%20or%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20floors%20and%20walls%2C%20I%20can%20put%20my%20back%20against%20the%20wall%20and%20push%20the%20structure%20to%20get%20it%20to%20move.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2cbdd90-c1b3-44e7-b8fe-1abf00d1e9d3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20bought%20the%20historic%20silo%20for%20%2490%2C000.%20It%20was%20decommissioned%20in%20the%201980s%20as%20part%20of%20an%20international%20treaty.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225817%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dozen%20black%20stools%20around%20a%20metal%20bar%20overlooking%20a%20massive%20entertainment%20space%20with%20a%20speakers%20on%20the%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740f4eefa0140cdd5650893%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20silo%20can%20turn%20into%20a%20nightclub%20that%20hosts%20parties%2C%20charity%20events%2C%20and%20even%20acrobats.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20GT%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20my%20missile%20silo%2C%20called%20Titan%20II%2C%20online.%20I%20started%20talking%20to%20the%20previous%20owner%20in%20January%20of%202010%2C%20and%20by%20August%2C%20I%20owned%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETitan%20II%20was%20denuclearized%20after%20the%20US%20and%20Russia%20signed%20a%201979%20treaty%20to%20limit%20each%20country's%20nuclear%20weapons.%20The%20US%20disarmed%20Titan%20II%20as%20part%20of%20that%20negotiation%2C%20called%20the%20Strategic%20Arms%20Limitation%20Talks%20II%20or%20SALT%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20to%20destroy%20the%20silo%20in%20very%20specific%20ways.%20They%20actually%20had%20to%20blow%20up%20the%20top%20of%20the%20structure%20and%20fill%20it%20in.%20So%20it%20was%20an%20underground%20structure%2C%20but%20completely%20buried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20the%20nine-acre%20site%20in%20Vilonia%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20for%20%2490%2C000%2C%20which%20was%20about%20a%20%2430%2C000%20premium%20over%20the%20land's%20value%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20three%20main%20components.%20There's%20the%20silo%20itself%2C%20a%2057-foot%20diameter%20structure%20or%20basically%20a%2015-story%20building%2C%20which%20sits%20underground%20at%20150%20feet%20deep.%20Then%20there's%20a%20long%20tunnel%20connecting%20the%20silo%20to%20the%20center%20area%20that's%2035%20feet%20underground.%20The%20last%20part%20of%20it%20is%20the%20launch%20control%20center%2C%20which%20goes%20as%20deep%20as%2050%20feet%20underground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22886f77c9-89c6-4233-9c2d-84aec42ec716%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20whole%20process%20was%20risky%20and%20expensive.%20I%20don't%20recommend%20people%20try%20to%20copy%20me.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Titan%20II%20bedroom%20with%20two%20queen%20beds%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740f3ceede4eeae3929223b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223994%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20middle%20floor%20of%20the%20control%20center%20is%20available%20to%20rent.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20GT%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20look%20at%20an%20old%20house%20and%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20way%20I%20want%20to%20rebuild%20that.%26quot%3B%20I%20liked%20the%20challenge.%20I%20knew%20we%20could%20build%20a%20pretty%20cool%20place.%20It%20just%20took%20a%20whole%20lot%20more%20money%20and%20time%20than%20I%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20finally%20got%20money%20and%20time%20together%20in%20October%202010.%20I%20rented%20a%20large%20bulldozer%20and%20an%20excavator%2C%20and%20then%20we%20started%20digging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20facility%20was%20full%20of%20water.%20We%20could%20see%20water%20pouring%20out%20on%20top%20of%20us%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20open%20the%20front%20door%20of%20the%20control%20center%20without%20dying.%20When%20the%20door%20popped%20open%2C%20a%20huge%20wave%20came%20over%20us.%20It%20was%20scary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225510%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20main%20bedroom%20of%20the%20silo%20with%20a%20king-sized%20bed%20and%20dual%20vanity%20sink..%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740f417fa0140cdd565082a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20main%20bedroom%20is%20in%20the%20livable%20portion%20of%20the%20silo.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20GT%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20other%20challenges.%20The%20place%20had%20asbestos%20and%20methane%20gas%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20control%20center%2C%20where%20the%20crew%20quarters%20were.%20I%20recorded%20videos%20of%20the%20whole%20process%2C%20and%20you%20can%20actually%20hear%20my%20voice%20change%20because%20of%20the%20methane%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20much%20more%20time%20than%20I%20did%20money.%20It's%20not%20that%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20to%20do%20it%2C%20but%20when%20you%20get%20the%20money%2C%20how%20do%20you%20prioritize%20using%20it%3F%20Do%20you%20throw%20it%20in%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20ground%20or%20spend%20it%20on%20a%20vacation%20for%20your%20family%3F%20Or%20upgrade%20the%20current%20home%20you%20live%20in%3F%20I%20had%20to%20make%20many%20of%20those%20decisions%20over%20the%2010-year%20renovation%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20%24800%2C000%2C%20we're%20probably%20netting%20%2480%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20revenue%20from%20the%20place%20now%20that%20I%20rent%20it%20out%20on%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20ask%20what%20the%20hardest%20part%20about%20doing%20this%20was%2C%20and%20it%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20work.%20It's%20the%20mental%20side.%20You're%20spending%20money%20on%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20you%20have%20nothing%20to%20show%20for%20it.%20It%20ended%20well%20for%20me%2C%20but%20the%20average%20person%20shouldn't%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20a%20great%20way%20to%20spend%20time%20or%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293b9748e-cd92-450a-87d9-5ee5cd00a61f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe've%20turned%20the%20missile%20into%20an%20Airbnb%20and%20have%20hosted%20YouTubers%2C%20acrobats%2C%20and%20a%20writer%20who%20lived%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20world%20for%2010%20days.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226003%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20gray%20and%20black%20modern%20kitchen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740f49afa0140cdd565086c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20main%20kitchen.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20GT%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20still%20live%20on%20the%20property%2C%20but%20we%20never%20moved%20in%20full-time.%20We'd%20spend%20some%20nights%20as%20a%20family%20there%2C%20either%20for%20fun%20or%20as%20a%20shelter%20from%20big%20tornadoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20walls%20and%20doors%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20real%20primary%20bedroom.%20The%20top%20floor%20has%20a%20king%20bed%2C%20a%20large%2C%20open%20shower%2C%20and%20a%20free-standing%20bathtub.%20The%20middle%20floor%20has%20two%20queen%20beds%20that%20we%20can%20move%20to%20make%20more%20space.%20Then%2C%20the%20kitchen%20and%20the%20living%20room%20are%20on%20the%20bottom%20floor%2C%20which%20also%20doubles%20as%20a%20dance%20floor%20and%20can%20turn%20into%20a%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20host%20anything%20on%20the%20property%2C%20including%20meetings.%20If%20it's%20semi-legal%20and%20people%20want%20to%20do%20it%20there%20and%20pay%20for%20it%2C%20we're%20fine%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20booking%20we%20got%20was%20in%20November%202020.%20It%20was%20a%20couple%20coming%20for%20their%20honeymoon%2C%20but%20they%20got%20a%20little%20too%20intoxicated%20at%20their%20wedding%20to%20make%20the%20trip.%20They%20sent%20their%20best%20man%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20initial%20rate%20was%20%24275%20per%20night%20with%20a%20%2475%20cleaning%20fee.%20Since%20then%2C%20we've%20raised%20prices%20a%20few%20times%2C%20so%20now%20we're%20in%20the%20%24400-%24700%20range%20for%20a%20one-night%20stay%2C%20depending%20on%20whether%20it's%20a%20weekday%20or%20a%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225977%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wooden%20bench%20and%20white%20marble%20tiles%20in%20the%20shower%20and%20bath%20portion%20of%20the%20main%20bedroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740f460ede4eeae39292276%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223986%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20one%20of%20the%20bathrooms.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20GT%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECOVID%20was%20obviously%20still%20going%20on%20when%20we%20started%20to%20list%20it%2C%20and%20I%20marketed%20the%20silo%20as%20the%20ultimate%20social%20distancing.%20There%20was%20this%20YouTube%20couple%2C%20Kara%20and%20Nate%2C%20with%20like%203%20million%20subscribers%2C%20who%20came%20to%20stay%20in%202021.%20They%20were%20travel%20influencers%20who%20started%20doing%20van%20life%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%2070%25%20of%20our%20bookings%20for%20the%20next%20year%20came%20through%20the%20video%20they%20made%20about%20their%20stay.%20Today%2C%20I%20would've%20paid%20an%20influencer%20couple%20like%20that%20%245%2C000%20to%20stay%20for%20that%20kind%20of%20exposure.%20With%20them%2C%20it%20was%20just%20a%20coincidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20once%20intentionally%20locked%20a%20woman%20in%20there%20for%2010%20days%20straight.%20In%202021%2C%20an%20author%20named%20Lynne%20Peeples%20called%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20doing%20a%20book%20on%20circadian%20rhythm%2C%20and%20I%20need%20a%20place%20that%20has%20absolutely%20no%20indication%20of%20time%20whatsoever.%26quot%3B%20She%20wanted%20to%20see%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20her%20sleep%20cycle.%20Before%20her%20arrival%2C%20I%20had%20to%20ensure%20everything%20that%20told%20the%20time%20was%20covered%3B%20even%20the%20Netflix%20account%20couldn't%20show%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20acrobats%20down%20there%20for%20a%20charity%20event.%20We've%20had%20bands%20perform.%20We've%20had%20birthday%20parties%20and%20even%20some%20swingers.%20I'm%20a%20pretty%20open%20guy.%20Just%20treat%20each%20other%20and%20the%20place%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20thing%20we%20haven't%20had%20yet%20is%20a%20wedding.%20And%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20reason%20for%20that%20is%20because%20of%20the%20stairs.%20It's%20five%20flights%20down%2C%20and%20typically%2C%20everybody's%20got%20at%20least%20one%20older%20relative%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20pretty%20terrible%20investment%2C%20any%20way%20you%20look%20at%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20become%20more%20than%20that.%20It's%20now%20part%20of%20my%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-renovated-a-missile-silo-airbnb-regrets-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732372123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740b295ede4eeae39290619%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-renovated-a-missile-silo-airbnb-regrets-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Air%20Force%20mechanic%20and%20tech%20professional%20GT%20Hill%20converted%20a%201980s%20missile%20silo%20into%20an%20Airbnb.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dlatu%40insider.com%20(Dan%20Latu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-renovated-a-missile-silo-airbnb-regrets-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAmerica%20Going%20Bankrupt%20Super%20Fast%26quot%3B%3A%20Elon%20Musk%20Offers%20Solution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20tasked%20by%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20excessive%20US%20spending%2C%20has%20warned%20that%20America%20could%20be%20nearing%20the%20verge%20of%20bankruptcy.%20The%20world's%20richest%20man%20and%20a%20close%20adviser%20of%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20been%20tasked%20to%20spearhead%20the%20newly%20created%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE)%20under%20the%20upcoming%20Republican%20administration%2C%20to%20find%20ways%20of%20saving%20taxpayer%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerica%20is%20currently%20headed%20for%20bankruptcy%20super%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Musk%20posted%20to%20X%20(formally%20Twitter)%2C%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20he%20bought%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20wrote%20this%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20on%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency's%20X%20handle%20that%20noted%20%26quot%3Bthe%20US%20Government%20spent%20USD%206.16.%20trillion%20while%20only%20bringing%20in%20USD%204.47%20trillion%26quot%3B%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAmerica%20is%20currently%20headed%20for%20bankruptcy%20super%20fast%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTm6JFJ6mef%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTm6JFJ6mef%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1860212805439488130%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20trend%20must%20be%20reversed%2C%20and%20we%20must%20balance%20the%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DOGE%20account%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20election%20campaign%2C%20one%20of%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20President-Elect%20Trump%20was%20the%20formation%20of%20DOGE%20to%20dismantle%20the%20government%20bureaucracy%20and%20cut%20wasteful%20spending.%C2%A0Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20while%20talking%20about%20skyrocketing%20US%20debts%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20had%20floated%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20Bitcoin%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpay%20off%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BUSD%2035%20trillion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President-elect%20is%20relying%20on%20two%20successful%20businessmen%20--%20Mr%20Musk%20and%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20--%20to%20dig%20into%20the%20details%20and%20give%20recommendations%20to%20his%20administration%20to%20restrict%20spending.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Forbes%2C%20the%20national%20debt%20of%20the%20US%20crossed%20the%20USD%2034%20trillion%20mark%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202024%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20Covid%20and%20lockdown%20stimulus%20measures%20that%20sent%20inflation%20spiralling%20and%20forced%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20to%20hike%20interest%20rates%20at%20a%20historical%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B..hand%20them%20a%20little%20crypto%20check%2C%20right%3F%20We'll%20hand%20them%20a%20little%20bitcoin%20and%20wipe%20out%20our%20USD%2035%20trillion%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fmikepatton%2F2024%2F11%2F20%2Ftrumps-department-of-government-efficiency-is-poised-to-cut-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Republicans%20won%20'Trifacta'%20of%20victories%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CExcess%20government%20spending%20is%20driving%20America%20into%20bankruptcy%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20debt%20growth%20is%20unsustainable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20DOGE%20department%20is%20a%20nod%20to%20the%202013%20famous%20Shiba%20Inu%20dog%20meme%2C%20which%20is%20also%20linked%20to%20the%20dogecoin%20cryptocurrency.%20According%20to%20Mr%20Musk%2C%20Dogecoin%20is%20his%20%26quot%3Bfavourite%26quot%3B%20cryptocurrency%20and%20is%20accepted%20as%20payment%20by%20his%20Tesla%20car%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBitcoin%20is%20a%20decentralised%20digital%20currency%20that%20operates%20without%20a%20financial%20system%20or%20government%20authorities.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investoped