ou%20looked%2C%20there%20was%20detail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20world%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20living%20around%20us%20and%20we%20were%20participating%20in%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20details%20helped%20Hechinger%20fully%20immerse%20himself%20in%20his%20role%20as%20Emperor%20Caracalla%2C%20one-half%20of%20the%20film's%20mercurial%2C%20unhinged%20ruling%20duo%20that%20turned%20Rome%20into%20a%20shadow%20of%20its%20former%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ea9fece-fe3b-40bd-94fd-d2aeefe49bfb%5C%22%3EHechinger's%20Caracalla%20is%20sick%20and%20twisted%20%E2%80%94%20a%20'dangerous%20concoction'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fred%20hechinger%2C%20pedro%20pascal%2C%20and%20joseph%20quinn%20as%20emperor%20caracalla%2C%20general%20acacius%2C%20and%20emperor%20geta%20in%20gladiator%20two.%20they're%20all%20clad%20in%20ornate%20robes%2C%20or%20in%20pascal's%20case%2C%20armor%2C%20and%20accepting%20acclaim%20from%20the%20gathered%20crowd%20in%20the%20colosseum%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672ec5345ec9bfa3d63cf3c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223317%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFred%20Hechinger%2C%20Pedro%20Pascal%2C%20and%20Joseph%20Quinn%20in%20%26quot%3BGladiator%20II.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAidan%20Monaghan%2FParamount%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGladiator%20II%26quot%3B%20is%20set%2015%20years%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Maximus%20Decimus%20Meridius%20(Russell%20Crowe).%20Under%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20villainous%20fraternal%20twin%20emperors%20Caracalla%20and%20Geta%20(Quinn)%2C%20Rome's%20citizens%20have%20become%20pawns%20and%20means%20for%20amusement.%20One%20of%20those%20gladiators%20forced%20to%20perform%20for%20them%20is%20Lucius%20(Mescal)%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Maximus%20and%20Lucilla%20(Connie%20Nielsen).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20twins%20show%20off%20their%20excess%20wealth%20in%20gold-adorned%20out