%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2025-wedding-trends-in-and-out-from-planner%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20wedding%20planner%2C%20I%20predict%20trends%20like%20live%20plants%2C%20live%20music%2C%20and%20photo%20booths%20will%20be%20in%20for%202025%20and%20grand%20entrances%20will%20be%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Elisabeth%20Kramer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2025-wedding-trends-in-and-out-from-planner%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BYou%20Will%20Have%20To%20Work%20Under%20D%20Fadnavis%26quot%3B%3A%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Jab%20At%20E%20Shinde%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERouted%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20election%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20was%20asked%20if%20this%20result%20has%20settled%20the%20debate%20over%20who%20represents%20the%20'real'%20Shiv%20Sena%20--%20he%20or%20his%20estranged%20lieutenant%20and%20the%20incumbent%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20whose%20government%20was%20toppled%20in%202022%20when%20Mr%20Shinde%20led%20a%20rebellion%20that%20split%20the%20Sena%2C%20had%20a%20message%20for%20his%20former%20brother-in-arms.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20work%20under%20(Devendra)%20Fadnavis.%20First%20figure%20out%20which%20bungalow%20you%20will%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20ongoing%20legal%20battle%20over%20which%20faction%20has%20claim%20to%20the%20Sena's%20symbol%20and%20name%20and%20lamented%20that%20the%20case%20had%20not%20reached%20a%20conclusion%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sena%20(UBT)%20has%20won%2020%20out%20of%20the%2089%20seats%20it%20contested%2C%20while%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20scored%2057%20out%20of%20the%2080%20seats%20it%20fought.%20The%20results%20were%20shocking%20when%20seen%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20just%20months%20ago.%20In%20the%20general%20election%2C%20the%20Sena%20(UBT)%20had%20won%20nine%20seats%20and%20Shinde%20Sena%20scored%20seven.%20And%20five%20months%20later%2C%20its%20tally%20is%20nowhere%20close%20to%20the%20breakaway%20faction's%20score.%20This%20would%20be%20disheartening%20for%20Team%20Thackeray%2C%20which%20was%20hoping%20its%20poll%20show%20would%20prove%20it%20was%20the%20'real'%20Sena.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%2C%20however%2C%20has%20raised%20a%20big%20question%20for%20Eknath%20Shinde%3A%20will%20he%20remain%20Chief%20Minister.%20When%20he%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20after%20the%202022%20mutiny%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20had%20become%20Chief%20Minister%20despite%20the%20BJP%20being%20the%20bigger%20party%20in%20the%20coalition.%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20had%20agreed%2C%20albeit%20grudgingly%2C%20to%20accept%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20scored%20a%20massive%20mandate%20by%20winning%20133%20out%20of%20the%20148%20seats%20it%20contested%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20claim%20the%20top%20post.%20What's%20more%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20has%20little%20to%20bargain%20because%20the%20BJP%20can%20still%20reach%20the%20majority%20mark%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20other%20ally%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP.%20This%20means%20Mr%20Shinde%20has%20little%20choice%20but%20to%20vacate%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20if%20the%20BJP%20asks%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20situation%20that%20Mr%20Thackeray%20referred%20to%20when%20he%20said%20Mr%20Shinde%20will%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bwork%20under%20Fadnavis%26quot%3B.%20The%20bungalow%20reference%20was%20also%20loaded%20because%20Mr%20Shinde%20will%20need%20to%20vacate%20Varsha%2C%20the%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20if%20he%20is%20not%20in%20the%20top%20post.%20The%20bungalow%20mention%20