nt%20amount%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20mega%20auction%2C%20and%20the%20mock%20auction%20conducted%20by%20auction%20broadcasters%20Star%20Sports%20and%20JioCinema%20showed%20that%20many%20cricket%20experts%20also%20believe%20the%20same.%20Coming%20up%20in%20the%20first%20set%20of%20marquee%20players%2C%20Pant%20was%20bought%20for%20a%20mind-boggling%20INR%2033%20crore%20by%20Punjab%20Kings%20(PBKS)%2C%20represented%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Eoin%20Morgan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F833-eoin-morgan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EEoin%20Morgan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fellow%20wicket-keeper%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20received%20an%20incredible%20sum%20of%20INR%2029.5%20crore%2C%20being%20purchased%20by%20Royal%20Challengers%20(RCB)%20represented%20by%20their%20former%20head%20coach%20Mike%20Hesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%20parted%20ways%20with%20Delhi%20Capitals%20(DC)%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPL%20mega%20auction%2C%20and%20has%20even%20clarified%20on%20social%20media%20that%20money%20wasn't%20the%20factor%20behind%20his%20decision.%20However%2C%20being%20arguably%20the%20biggest%20name%20in%20the%20auction%2C%20Pant%20is%20still%20expected%20to%20fetch%20a%20huge%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPBKS%20boast%20the%20highest%20auction%20purse%20of%20any%20team%2C%20with%20Rs%20110.5%20cr%2C%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20go%20all-out%20for%20Pant%20with%20former%20DC%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ricky%20Ponting%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F348-ricky-ponting-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERicky%20Ponting%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20anticipated%20his%20price%20to%20soar%20between%20Rs%2026%20and%20Rs%2029%20crore%2C%20but%20his%20eventual%20price%20was%20a%20record-shattering%20Rs%2033%20crore%E2%80%94deservedly%20so.%20Rishabh%20is%20not%20just%20a%20top-order%20left-handed%20batsman%20but%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20explosive%20players%20in%20modern%20cricket.%20Coupled%20with%20his%20captaincy%20credentials%20and%20the%20potential%20to%20serve%20for%20years%20to%20come%2C%20he's%20akin%20to%20securing%20a%20young%20MS%20Dhoni.%20This%20is%20a%20strategic%20long-term%20investment%2C%20focused%20on%20building%20a%20robust%20foundation%20for%20the%20future.%20In%20my%20view%2C%20players%20like%20Pant%20are%20simply%20invaluable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Morgan%2C%20in%20the%20mock%20auction%20hosted%20by%20Star%20Sports%20and%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20KL%20Rahul's%20stock%20may%20also%20be%20higher%20following%20a%20very%20impressive%20showing%20in%20the%20ongoing%20India-Australia%20first%20Test%20at%20Perth.%20Rahul%20chose%20to%20enter%20the%20auction%20pool%20instead%20of%20staying%20at%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRCB%20would%20ideally%20prioritize%20Rishabh%20Pant%20to%20ensure%20continuity%20after%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20especially%20for%20long-term%20stability.%20I%20personally%20bid%20up%20to%20%E2%82%B932.5%20crore%20for%20Pant%20but%20wouldn't%20have%20stretched%20as%20much%20for%20KL%20Rahul.%20At%2032%2C%20Rahul%20brings%20experience%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20anchor%20the%20innings%20post-Virat's%20era.%20As%20a%20local%20talent%2C%20he%20also%20fills%20the%20critical%20wicket-keeping%20slot%20left%20vacant%20by%20DK's%20exit.%20While%20RCB%20would%20likely%20bid%20aggressively%20for%20him%2C%20the%20final%20price%20would%20hinge%20on%20the%20dynamics%20and%20unpredictability%20of%20the%20auction%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hesson%20after%20acquiring%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReigning%20IPL%20champions%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%2C%20represented%20in%20the%20mock%20auction%20by%20former%20player%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanjay%20Bangar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117-sanjay-bangar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Bangar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bought%20back%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Rs%2021%20cr.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20Venky%20Mysore's%20swift%20auction%20tactics%E2%80%94raising%20the%20paddle%20decisively%20when%20targeting%20a%20player.%20My%20reasoning%20was%20clear%3A%20Shreyas%20is%20a%20proven%20winning%20captain%2C%20and%20in%20a%20dynamic%20format%20like%20T20%2C%20such%20leadership%20is%20invaluable.%20If%20KKR%20chose%20to%20release%20him%2C%20it%20might%20have%20been%20due%20to%20financial%20considerations%2C%20possibly%20Shreyas%20demanding%20a%20higher%20price%20that%20didn't%20align%20with%20their%20valuation.%20The%20auction%20provided%20an%20opportunity%20to%20test%20his%20market%20worth.%20Yes%2C%20I%20exceeded%20the%20ideal%20budget%2C%20allocating%20over%2015%25%20of%20the%20purse%20for%20a%20captain.%20However%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20his%20caliber%20strengthens%20the%20team%20immensely%2C%20fostering%20critical%20partnerships%20with%20management%2C%20Chandrakant%20Pandit%2C%20and%20the%20support%20staff.%20For%20me%2C%20continuity%20in%20leadership%20holds%20unparalleled%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bangar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20big%20purchases%20in%20Star%20Sports%2FJioCinema%20mock%20auction%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Starc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1416-mitchell-starc-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Starc%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Rs%2018%20cr%20-%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshdeep%20Singh%3A%20Rs%2016.5%20cr%20-%20Punjab%20Kings%20(PBKS)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuzvendra%20Chahal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsport