w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FUdhay-vijayan_11zon-1731927501-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380798%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221757%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUday%20Vijayan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Beyond%20Carlton%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20words%2C%20etched%20in%20Uday%E2%80%99s%20memory%2C%20pushed%20him%20to%20establish%20Beyond%20Carlton%20a%20few%20months%20after%20the%20incident.%20Beyond%20Carlton%20is%20a%20citizen-led%20non-profit%20organisation%20primarily%20focusing%20on%20creating%20awareness%20regarding%20fire%20safety%20and%20ensuring%20that%20every%20building%20has%20necessary%20measures%20installed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20the%20group%20filed%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20%2C%20requesting%20for%20mandatory%20inspections%20of%20high%20rise%20apartments%20(15%20m%20and%20above)%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20court%20passed%20necessary%20orders%20instructing%20the%20Karnataka%20Government%20to%20implement%20the%20same.%20A%20notification%20to%20re-inspect%20the%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20(NOC)%20every%20two%20years%20was%20also%20implemented.%20Functioning%20on%20three%20pillars%20%E2%80%94%20accountability%2C%20awareness%2C%20and%20advocacy%20%E2%80%94%20their%20efforts%20provided%20a%20different%20lens%20regarding%20fire%20safety%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUday%20and%20his%20team%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20also%20saw%20the%20sanctioning%20of%20funds%20for%20firefighters%20to%20have%20a%20separate%20fire%20inspection%20department%20to%20investigate%20when%20a%20fire%20incident%20occurs.%20This%20was%20crucial%20because%20it%20allowed%20firefighters%20to%20access%20the%20accident%20zone%20sooner%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20investigate%20and%20determine%20the%20cause%20of%20such%20catastrophes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20fire-safe%20Bengaluru%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20Government%20planned%20to%20develop%20blueprints%20to%20tackle%20multiple%20issues%20in%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CBeyond%20Carlton%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20related%20to%20fire%20safety%20as%20nobody%20considered%20fire%20a%20crucial%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Uday.%20The%20group%2C%20along%20with%20Janaagraha%2C%20an%20NGO%2C%20and%20the%20Karnataka%20Fire%20and%20Emergency%20Services%2C%20came%20up%20with%20a%20blueprint%20focused%20on%20three%20elements%20%E2%80%94%20capacity%20building%2C%20regulation%20and%20compliance%2C%20and%20awareness%20creation%20%E2%80%94%20to%20eliminate%20fire%20accidents%20in%20the%20city%20aimed%20at%20making%20the%20city%20100%25%20fire-safe!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20blueprint%20was%20ambitious%2C%20but%20every%20plan%20had%20to%20be%20to%20achieve%20at%20least%2050%25%20of%20what%20we%20had%20envisioned%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gopal%20Devanahalli%2C%20a%20trustee%20who%20had%20lost%20one%20of%20his%20friends%20in%20the%20Carton%20tragedy.%20Beyond%20Carlton%E2%80%99s%20fire%20safety%20blueprint%20was%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20aware%20of%20how%20to%20act%20when%20there%20is%20a%20fire.%20Through%20our%20awareness%20workshops%20in%20association%20with%20estate%20managers%20and%20the%20Bengaluru%20Apartment%20Federation%2C%20we%20can%20educate%20people%20about%20the%20necessary%20measures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gopal%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20had%20previous%20corporate%20experience%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20make%20strategic%20decisions%20on%20the%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20fire%20department%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uday%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20issues%20the%20team%20identified%20was%20the%20involvement%20of%20multiple%20departments%20and%20government%20authorities%20in%20a%20fire%20accident.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20fire%20accidents%20happen%20due%20to%20short-circuiting%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20control%20of%20BESCOM%2C%E2%80%9D%20Venkitachalam%2C%20a%20trustee%2C%20elaborates.%20Building%20owners%2C%20citizens%2C%20BBMP%2C%20NDRF%2C%20police%2C%20and%20fire%20departments%20are%20others%20involved%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201152px)%20100vw%2C%201152px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20workshop%20on%20fire%20safety%20being%20held%20in%20Hulimavu%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awareness-and-prevention-day-feb-23-Hulimavu-FS-1731926410-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FFire-awarenes